data.description: Incredible Investment Opportunity! This property offers a fantastic chance to own a home and generate rental income from the upstairs unit. The lower unit boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and includes a beautifully renovated bar space in the basement, perfect for entertaining or additional income potential. The upper unit features 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom, offering picturesque water views, making it an attractive rental option. The property also features multiple fenced areas, providing privacy and security for both units. Plus, it was tastefully renovated in 2017, ensuring a modern and inviting atmosphere for residents. Don't miss this chance to own a property that not only provides a comfortable living space but also offers an excellent opportunity for generating rental income!
